'''直頜青鱂'''（[[學名|學名]]：'''''Oryzias orthognathus'''''）是[[異鱂科|異鱂科]][[青鱂屬|青鱂屬]]下的一種[[淡水魚|淡水魚]]，原産於[[蘇拉威西島|蘇拉威西島]]的[[婆娑湖|婆娑湖]]中。<ref name=IUCN>{{cite web|title=Oryzias orthognathus|url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/15577/0|publisher=International Union for Conservation of Nature and Natural Resources|accessdate=31 May 2013|archive-date=2018-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602114549/http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/15577/0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==描述==

直頜青鱂的平均大小為{{convert|5|cm|in}}，並不是每年都進行繁殖。<ref name=FishBase>{{cite web|title=Oryzias orthognathus  Kottelat, 1990 Sharpjawed buntingi|url=http://fishbase.sinica.edu.tw/Summary/SpeciesSummary.php?id=6268|publisher=Fish Base|accessdate=31 May 2013|archive-date=2017-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117002101/http://fishbase.sinica.edu.tw/Summary/SpeciesSummary.php?id=6268|dead-url=no}}</ref>

